  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Glow Berry Mousse</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Glow Berry Mousse</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Warly\" title=\"Warly\">Warly</a> specific <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">item</a> cooked in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\">Portable Crock Pot</a> that is exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>.\n</p><p>It requires either two <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lesser_Glow_Berry\" title=\"Lesser Glow Berry\">Lesser Glow Berries</a> or one <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Glow_Berry\" title=\"Glow Berry\">Glow Berry</a>, and a total Fruits value of 2.0 or higher. Filler can not be <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Inedible\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Inedible\">Inedible</a>. Note that the two Lesser Glow Berries or one Glow Berry both count for 1 Fruit value. Adding two or more <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Durian\" title=\"Durian\">Durians</a> may result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Tartare\" title=\"Monster Tartare\">Monster Tartare</a>.\n</p><p>When eaten, it causes the consumer to generate a large amount of light (about as much as a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Torch\" title=\"Torch\">Torch</a>), with the light decaying slowly over the course of 2 days.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lesser_Glow_Berry\" title=\"Lesser Glow Berry\"><img alt=\"Lesser Glow Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lesser_Glow_Berry.png?9ddfc0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\"><img alt=\"Fruit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fruit.png?853057\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>x<b>1.0</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Portable Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Portable_Crock_Pot.png/42px-Portable_Crock_Pot.png?f4c0d3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Glow_Berry_Mousse\" title=\"Glow Berry Mousse\"><img alt=\"Glow Berry Mousse.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Glow_Berry_Mousse.png?c69fa4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Glow_Berry\" title=\"Glow Berry\"><img alt=\"Glow Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Glow_Berry.png?8b8a71\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\"><img alt=\"Fruit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fruit.png?853057\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>x<b>1.0</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Portable Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Portable_Crock_Pot.png/42px-Portable_Crock_Pot.png?f4c0d3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Glow_Berry_Mousse\" title=\"Glow Berry Mousse\"><img alt=\"Glow Berry Mousse.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Glow_Berry_Mousse.png?c69fa4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>Fillers cannot be <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Inedible\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Inedible\">Inedible</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lesser_Glow_Berry\" title=\"Lesser Glow Berry\"><img alt=\"Lesser Glow Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lesser_Glow_Berry.png?9ddfc0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lesser_Glow_Berry\" title=\"Lesser Glow Berry\"><img alt=\"Lesser Glow Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lesser_Glow_Berry.png?9ddfc0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td>