  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\nGlow Berry Mousse\nFood Info\n37.5\n3\n10\nVeggie\nObject Info\nPerk\nEmits light upon consumption.\n8 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx2 x1.0 x1\nx1 x1.0 x2\nCan be Cooked only in Portable Crock Pot\n20\n30\nMiscellaneous\n\"glowberrymousse\"\n“Warly sure can cook.”\n–Wilson\n“That's definitely going in my mouth.”\n–Willow\n“Tasty-making friend has made thing very tasty.”\n–Wolfgang\n“It swirls like the endless abyss.”\n–Wendy\n“HIGH QUALITY MINION FUEL”\n–WX-78\n“A brand new recipe I see. Marvelous!”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Boy would I ever like to dig into that.”\n–Woodie\n“What a nice change it is to know someone who cooks.”\n–Maxwell\n“A repulsive vegetable cöncöctiön.”\n–Wigfrid\n“Mmm, mousse!”\n–Webber\n“My own special recipe!”\n–Warly\n“Glowy chomp-stuff”\n–Wormwood\n“You really outdid yourself with this one, buddy.”\n–Winona\n“Seems like a lot of effort for something you eat.”\n–Wortox\n“Oooh, it glowing!!”\n–Wurt\n“Will my insides light up if I eat it?”\n–Walter\n“What a delightfully useful dessert!”\n–Wanda\nGlow Berry Mousse is a Warly specific Food item cooked in the Portable Crock Pot that is exclusive to Don't Starve Together.\nIt requires either two Lesser Glow Berries or one Glow Berry, and a total Fruits value of 2.0 or higher. Filler can not be Meats or Inedible. Note that the two Lesser Glow Berries or one Glow Berry both count for 1 Fruit value. Adding two or more Durians may result in Monster Tartare.\nWhen eaten, it causes the consumer to generate a large amount of light (about as much as a Torch), with the light decaying slowly over the course of 2 days.\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n×2\nx1.0\nx1.0\n×2\nFillers cannot be Meats or Inedible.\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n×2\n50% chance of producing Monster Tartare\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nIcon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
