  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|foodRecipe ={{Pic|32px|Lesser Glow Berry}}x2 {{Pic|32px|Fruit}}x1.0 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x1<hr>{{Pic|32px|Glow Berry}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Fruit}}x1.0 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x2\n|foodPortableCrockPot = 1\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodType = [[Veggie]] [[File:Veggie.png|32px|]]\n|icon = {{FULLPAGENAME}}.png\n|image = {{FULLPAGENAME}} Dropped.png\n|hpRestored = 3\n|hungerRestored = 37.5\n|sanityRestored = 10\n|cooktime = 20\n|priority = 30\n|spoil = 8 Days\n|stack = 40\n|spawnCode = \"glowberrymousse\"\n|perk = Emits [[light sources|light]] upon consumption.\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Warly sure can cook.\n|willow = That's definitely going in my mouth.\n|wolfgang = Tasty-making friend has made thing very tasty.\n|wendy = It swirls like the endless abyss.\n|wx78 = HIGH QUALITY MINION FUEL\n|wickerbottom = A brand new recipe I see. Marvelous!\n|woodie = Boy would I ever like to dig into that.\n|maxwell = What a nice change it is to know someone who cooks.\n|wigfrid = A repulsive vegetable cöncöctiön.\n|webber = Mmm, mousse!\n|winona = You really outdid yourself with this one, buddy.\n|warly = My own special recipe!\n|wortox = Seems like a lot of effort for something you eat.\n|wormwood = Glowy chomp-stuff\n|wurt = Oooh, it glowing!!\n|walter = Will my insides light up if I eat it?\n|wanda = What a delightfully useful dessert!\n|choose = walter}}\n'''Glow Berry Mousse''' is a [[Warly]] specific [[Food]] [[item]] cooked in the [[Portable Crock Pot]] that is exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]''.\n\nIt requires either two [[Lesser Glow Berry|Lesser Glow Berries]] or one [[Glow Berry]], and a total Fruits value of 2.0 or higher. Filler can not be [[Meats]] or [[Inedible]]. Note that the two Lesser Glow Berries or one Glow Berry both count for 1 Fruit value. Adding two or more [[Durian]]s may result in [[Monster Tartare]].\n\nWhen eaten, it causes the consumer to generate a large amount of light (about as much as a [[Torch]]), with the light decaying slowly over the course of 2 days.\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Lesser Glow Berry\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Fruit\n|comparator2=x\n|count2=1.0\n|item3 = Filler\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Glow Berry Mousse}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Glow Berry\n|item2 = Fruit\n|comparator2 = x\n|count2 = 1.0\n|item3 = Filler\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Glow Berry Mousse\n|note = Fillers cannot be [[Meats]] or [[Inedible]].\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Lesser Glow Berry\n|item2 = Lesser Glow Berry\n|item3 = Lesser Glow Berry\n|item4 = Lesser Glow Berry\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Glow Berry Mousse}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Lesser Glow Berry\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Berry\n|item3 = Berry\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Glow Berry Mousse}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Glow Berry\n|item2 = Durian\n|item3 = Egg\n|item4 = Ice\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Glow Berry Mousse\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Glow Berry\n|item2 = Durian\n|item3 = Durian\n|item4 = Durian\n|tool = Portable Crock Pot\n|result = Glow Berry Mousse\n|note = 50% chance of producing [[Monster Tartare]]\n}}\n{{clear}}\n<!--\n== {{Pic32|Placeholder}} Trivia==\n-->\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nGlow Berry Mousse 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\n</gallery>\n{{Edible Items}}\n[[Category:Food]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Portable Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[zh:发光浆果慕斯]]"
